<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The System thread id is not the underlying OS tid. To get the underlying OS tid please use <ref refid="group__THREADS_1ga190c8d53ca36e6a454878a81af6d2630" kindref="member">PIN_GetNativeTid()</ref>.</para>
